# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# PathForge API — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# All values shown below are safe defaults for local development.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Brand Identity ──────────────────────────────────────────────
APP_NAME=PathForge
APP_SLUG=pathforge
APP_TAGLINE=Career Intelligence for Everyone
APP_VERSION=0.1.0

# ── Server ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
DEBUG=false
ENVIRONMENT=development

# ── Database (PostgreSQL + pgvector) ────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/pathforge_dev
DATABASE_ECHO=false
# DATABASE_SSL: leave UNSET for auto-derivation (ADR-0001).
#   - ENVIRONMENT=production → TLS on automatically.
#   - ENVIRONMENT=development/testing → TLS off.
#   - Explicit DATABASE_SSL=false in production is rejected at boot.
#   - Do NOT put ?sslmode=require in DATABASE_URL; it is stripped with
#     a warning. TLS is controlled only through this variable.
# (Uncomment only when overriding the auto-derivation.)
#DATABASE_SSL=true

# ── Redis ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
# REDIS_SSL: leave UNSET for auto-derivation (ADR-0002).
#   - ENVIRONMENT=production → TLS on automatically.
#   - ENVIRONMENT=development/testing → TLS off.
#   - Explicit REDIS_SSL=false in production is rejected at boot.
#   - REDIS_URL=rediss://... + REDIS_SSL=false in production is also
#     rejected (conflicting TLS directives, ADR-0002).
#   - In dev, rediss:// scheme wins and upgrades the flag automatically.
# (Uncomment only when overriding the auto-derivation.)
#REDIS_SSL=true

# ── JWT Authentication ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Dev defaults below are NOT production-safe but are deliberately NOT
# the strings the config validator rejects in production — so local boot
# is warning-free. Generate production secrets with:
#     openssl rand -hex 32   (≥ 32 bytes, unique per secret)
JWT_SECRET=dev-jwt-secret-local-only-do-not-deploy-abcdef0123456789
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=dev-jwt-refresh-local-only-do-not-deploy-fedcba9876543210
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=60
JWT_REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRE_DAYS=30

# ── CORS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated origins (parsed as JSON list in settings)
# CORS_ORIGINS=["http://localhost:3000","http://localhost:5173"]

# ── AI / LLM API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your keys from the respective provider dashboards:
# - Anthropic: https://console.anthropic.com/
# - Google AI: https://aistudio.google.com/
# - Voyage AI: https://dash.voyageai.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=
VOYAGE_API_KEY=

# ── LiteLLM Tiered Model Routing ───────────────────────────────
# Models are tier-based and swappable without code changes.
# Primary (80%): workhorse for CV gen, match explanations
# Fast (15%): high-volume parsing, classification
# Deep (5%): complex career DNA analysis only
LLM_PRIMARY_MODEL=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-20250514
LLM_FAST_MODEL=gemini/gemini-2.0-flash
LLM_DEEP_MODEL=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-20250514
LLM_TIMEOUT=60
LLM_MAX_RETRIES=3

# ── Voyage AI Embeddings ────────────────────────────────────────
VOYAGE_MODEL=voyage-3
VOYAGE_EMBED_BATCH_SIZE=128

# ── Rate Limiting ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Per-user limits on AI endpoints (expensive LLM calls)
RATE_LIMIT_PARSE=30/minute
RATE_LIMIT_EMBED=20/minute
RATE_LIMIT_MATCH=30/minute
RATE_LIMIT_TAILOR=10/minute
# Use redis:// URI for production rate limiting
RATELIMIT_STORAGE_URI=memory://

# ── Job Aggregation Providers ───────────────────────────────────
# Adzuna: https://developer.adzuna.com/ (register for app_id + app_key)
ADZUNA_APP_ID=
ADZUNA_APP_KEY=
# Jooble: https://jooble.org/api/about (register for API key)
JOOBLE_API_KEY=

# ── Sentry Error Tracking (Sprint 30) ───────────────────────
# Get DSN from: https://pathforge.sentry.io/settings/projects/pathforge-api/keys/
SENTRY_DSN=
SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT=development
SENTRY_TRACES_SAMPLE_RATE=1.0

# ── Logging ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
LOG_LEVEL=INFO

# ── Cloudflare Turnstile (Sprint 39) ────────────────────────
# Secret key from https://dash.cloudflare.com → Turnstile
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY=

# ── OAuth Providers (Sprint 39) ─────────────────────────────
# Google: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
# Microsoft: https://portal.azure.com → App registrations
MICROSOFT_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
MICROSOFT_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=

# ── Email (Resend) ──────────────────────────────────────────
RESEND_API_KEY=
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=PathForge <hello@pathforge.eu>
RESEND_AUDIENCE_ID=

# ── Stripe Billing (Sprint 34) ──────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
